casebody.data:
State ex rel. Fhiaras
v.
Gaul 2018-0574 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 13, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

In Mandamus. On relator's motion to strike respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion denied. Sua sponte, respondent ordered to immediately serve a copy of the motion to dismiss on relator. Relator may file a response to the motion within ten days.
